---

For the human/agent collaboration model on this repository, see
docs/ARCHITECTURE.md Part 5 ("User Contributions That Shaped the Design")
and Part 6 ("Advisor's Role"). The project is explicitly human-in-the-loop:
the agent contributes synthesis and drafting; the human contributes
direction, judgment, empirical correction, and approval gates.
